    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "counselors and advisors dont change the facts though. the money is gone. it's not just a math problem, it's like... my whole life is just a series of failures now. my family, my work, everything is tied to this debt. i feel like i've already lost everything, so whats even the point in trying to fix it? it just feels like a slow death anyway.",
